Just noticed something.  Isn't glance-image-import.conf an optional file, and we only keep the sample around?

Also, some of the list options have bounds=True and some don't.  We should probably be consistent.  I think i'd prefer bounds=True, although it looks like when oslo.config generates the commented-out default value, it doesn't include the [ ] even when bounds=True.
